title: It Aint Pretty (Full Doc) Best Women Surfers

sources.title: It Aint Pretty (Full Doc) Best Women Surfers
sources.description:
A documentary about the challenges and triumphs of female big wave surfers fighting sexism in the water, in competition, in the media and in the surf industry with the support of a closely-knit community of like- minded women. This film takes you inside a growing movement of women that are shattering the images of female surfers in the media.

Director Dayla Soul
2016     
Edited for YouTube ad standards
